HEADWORD: Benting time
<hw>Bent"ing time"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>The season when pigeons are
said to feed on bents, before peas are ripe.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Bare <qex>benting times</qex> . . . may come.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>bentonite</ent>⟦br⟧
